  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个缓存系统的处理流程图。核心是从读取trace开始，然后检查请求是否有效，接着去缓存里查找。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ReadTrace",
        "ReqValid",
        "CacheGet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以起点是Read trace，然后有个判断节点Request is Valid，如果无效就直接结束，有效的话再走Cache Get对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ReadTrace",
        "ReqValid",
        "END",
        "CacheGet"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个逻辑。Cache Get之后还要判断Found，没找到的话就是miss，需要处理插入。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CacheGet",
        "Found",
        "miss"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画主干：Read trace → Request is Valid → Cache Get → Found判断。miss分支我往下画。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ReadTrace",
        "ReqValid",
        "CacheGet",
        "Found",
        "miss"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "miss之后需要判断缓存有没有空间，这个节点叫Cache Has Space? 可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "miss",
        "CacheHasSpace"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，有空间就直接Insert To Cache，没空间要先Evict From Cache再插入。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CacheHasSpace",
        "Insert",
        "EvictCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Evict From Cache之后是连到Insert，还是两个都有输出？另外eviction本身要不要触发什么操作？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EvictCache",
        "Insert",
        "OnEviction"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Evict From Cache要输出到Insert，同时eviction本身要触发On Eviction这个回调。所以EvictCache有两个出口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EvictCache",
        "Insert",
        "OnEviction"
